description: Mr. Sugar Rush is Dallas and Fort Worth’s elite ice cream truck of the future. We serve the entire DFW metro area and surrounding cities! We custom build our ice cream trucks with a five star visual presentation in mind. The words out of our customers’ mouths are “This is the biggest and best ice cream truck I’ve ever seen.” Top notch service and serving equipment! Two fully equipped trucks and even portable kiosks are available for your party needs!
name: Mr. Sugar Rush
